textAnnotations.description:
Audi Centre Cairns 6 Day Demonstrator Event.
Last chance, sale ending soon.
Audi Centre Cairns
Now is the time to discover unprecedented offers across a wide range of models, visit Audi Centre Cairns before August 12, 2017 to take advantage of this incredible opportunity.
Visit us to receive exceptional offers across a range of demonstrator models, including:
Complimentary registration, CTP and stamp duty*
Complimentary 3 years/45,000kms Scheduled
Servicing
Exceptionally Low Finance available on all
demonstrators.
A1 Sportback MY16 Sport $96.63 Per Week
Xenon headlights with LED daytime running
Lights, 17" 5-spoke alloys, keyless entry and start
Visit Audi Centre Cairns today to find out more.
303-309 Mulgrave Road, Cairns | Tel. 4046 6322 | audicentrecairns.com.au
"Free Rego, Free CTP, Free Stamp Duty on all My16 demos and selected MY17 demos only. The offer is calculated based on the drive away RRP. Not available with any other offer or to fleet, government, rental buyers, hire car and chauffeur. $32,290
drive away price relates to demo MY16 Audi A1 Sportback SN:650252. Based on a 4.49% p.a. comparison rate and drive away price of $32,290 for SN:650252 with the Audi secured consumer loan term of 60 months, 10% deposit & balloon of 30%.
Excludes any insurance products. Vehicle must be sold during the sale event ending 12/08/17, customer must take delivery by 31/08/17. T&Cs, fees & charges apply. Full terms and conditions are available on application. AFS" reserves the right to
extend, withdraw or change this offer. 4.49% p.a. comparison rate available to approved personal applicants of Audi Financial Services (AFS)". "AFS is a trading name of Volkswagen Financial Services Australia Pty Limited ABN 20 097 071 460, Australian
Credit Licence Number 389344. Complimentary 3 Year/45,000 km (whichever occurs first servicing applies to the first 3 standard scheduled services of your vehicle from the date of first registration. 3 Year/45,000 km service are scheduled to occur
at every 15,000 km/12 month interval (whichever occurs first) as stated in the Service Schedule and excludes wear and tear items and additional work or components required. Customer must comply with scheduled servicing intervals. Available on all
MY16 Demonstrator models only.
